cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. 

This paper is about a neural network for question answering, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses attention mechanism and prediction layer, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it focuses on finding the most relevant answer choice based on the query and passage. Finally, the use of neural networks suggests that it could also fall under the sub-category of neural networks (cs.NE).
